    "As high-level principles continue to emerge, there is also a rise in resources addressing AI ethics.",
    "However, it remains problematic to determine which tool could aid adherence to these principles (Corrêa 2021; Morley et al. 2020).",
    "Understanding the Collingridge dilemma is crucial in AI ethics, especially when exploring how technology ethics and values interact.",
    "This concept highlights the intricate link between technologies and the frameworks we use to judge them.",
    "The ethical side of the Collingridge dilemma poses an ongoing challenge: navigating a constantly changing landscape where technologies reshape societal values and ethical standards (Kudina and Verbeek 2019)."
